content.shortDescription: Burger with 2 Pieces of Hot & Crispy Boneless, 1 Portion of Chips, 1 Regular Potato & Gravy and 1 Regular Drink.
content.longDescription: When you bite down on the Zinger Crunch Burger™, here’s what you’ll be sinking your teeth into, in descending order: Bun, jalapeno mayo, corn chips (crunch), cheese, Zinger Fillet (more crunch), slaw, jalapeno mayo, bun. And that’s just the Burger – you’ve also got regular Chips, a Drink, our famous Potato & Gravy and 2 Hot & Crispy™ Boneless pieces to enjoy. You’re welcome. Not everywhere and not forever.
